text: Craig A. Gagnon (born August 2, 1960) is an American politician. He is a member of the South Carolina House of Representatives from the 11th District, serving since 2013. He is a member of the Republican party. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1960 births Category:Members of the South Carolina House of Representatives Category:South Carolina Republicans Category:Politicians from Lowell, Massachusetts Category:21st-century American politicians
